{{danquote|Like the unique African Baobab tree, which nourishes its community with its leaves and fruit, McDonald’s has branched out to the niggers community nourishing it with valuable "programs" and "opportunities".|You now have the opportunity to mop floors and fry potatoes!}}

Perhaps [[McDonalds]] thinks Martin Luther King Jr day isn't enough. Or maybe they think that [[shit nobody cares about|black history month]] just doesn't have enough days. Whatever the case, they decided to act on this [[hatred|passion]] for black people by creating a website designed to celebrate [[black people]] every [[WRYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYY|fucking day of the year]] and further confirmed that black people are so stupid they need to be given [[welfare|as much help as possible]].

[[365Black.com]] (aka [http://365nigger.com 365nigger.com]) is a website run by the [[McDonalds]] Corporation designed to inform the African American community about their delicious fried chickens.  It also helps to show that McDonald's is [[not racist]] because they have a website for [[niggers]].

When asked about a possibility of a 365white.com, a spokesperson responded that it would be very [[racist]] and unethical to make a website for white people.  Aren't [[Hypocrisy|double standards]] great?

==Employment Opportunities!==
[[File:Formerly_obese_man.jpg|thumb|right|Like this man, you have the "opportunity" to become formerly obese as well.]]

Since McDonald's knew that our [[Black]] friends are [[Retarded|employment-challenged]], they knew that a major potential work force was sitting on their couch collecting welfare checks. They decided to take advantage of this fact and created 365Black.com. What better way to increase chicken McNugget (The poor man's fried chicken) sales and sheep-like, low level employees than to reach out to them through the [[internets]].

{{danquote|About 40% of our owner/operators are minorities and women.|McDonalds, on affirmative action.}}

McDonalds is very fond of the darkies and created this program to help them from under the oppressive boot of ''[[Conspiracy Theory|the man]]''. Such job opportunities include flipping burgers, manning the cash register(don't worry black people, no math needed and all of the buttons are large pictures!), drive through attendant and mopping the floors. They also offer opportunities to purchase franchising rights but that is just a funny joke by McDonalds (HA HA McDonalds you are always joking).

==[[Centipede filled vagina|Ulterior motives....in ''my'' giant faceless corporation????]]==
When McDonalds isn't hiring [[Mexicans]] that can't speak English, they turn their attention to America's other favorite minority. They figured out that they could kill two birds with one stone by first pandering to blacks to increase sales and steal KFC's profits. [http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/28300393/ McDonalds is already abundant in urban areas] Thus they could commence step two to lure them en masse. Their second motive was to [[slavery|employ]] them. Their entire operation was set up in the beginning to control their lives through regulation of their diet and income. Since Black people are stupid, they of course bought in and McDonalds is now succeeding in their plot to keep the black man down. 

==365white.com==
As you are aware, there is sadly no 365white.com (or 365yellow.com or 365red.com or 365brown.com etc.). If McDonalds were to create such a website, it would be extremely [[awesome|racist]] and Al Sharpton might get mad and make a speech about it or even write letters! We all know that there are absolutely no white people in poverty and white people have no [[Europe|interesting]] [[WW2|history]] or [[Nazis|culture]] that could possibly be [[party hard|celebrated]]. On the other hand, blacks have things like peanut butter, [[unfunny|Eddie Murphy]], and [[basketball]]!!!! They deserve a website because remember that time whites went to [[Africa]] and [[Shit nobody cares about|made them slaves]]. McDonalds is such a [[evil|good]] corporation for helping them like this. Whites are all so over-privileged. 
 
